Expert to USB

Download (for everybody)
========================

1. Download ISO image:

       wget http://dl.amnesia.boum.org/tails/stable/tails-i386-1.6/tails-i386-1.6.iso

If you have an OpenPGP key
==========================

1. Import Tails signing key

       wget https://tails.boum.org/tails-signing.key

       gpg --import < tails-signing.key

1. Install Debian keyring

       sudo apt-get install debian-keyring/jessie

1. Import OpenPGP key of Zack:

       gpg --keyring=/usr/share/keyrings/debian-keyring.gpg --export zack@debian.org | gpg --import

1. Verify that Tails signing key is certified by Zack:

       gpg --check-sigs A490D0F4D311A4153E2BB7CADBB802B258ACD84F

1. Certify Tails signing with your own key:

       gpg --sign-key A490D0F4D311A4153E2BB7CADBB802B258ACD84F

1. Verify ISO image:

       gpg --verify tails-i386-1.6.1.iso.sig tails-i386-1.6.1.iso

   Expected output:

       gpg:                using RSA key 0x98FEC6BC752A3DB6
       gpg: Good signature from "Tails developers (offline long-term identity key) <tails@boum.org>" [full]
       gpg:                 aka "Tails developers <tails@boum.org>" [full]
       Primary key fingerprint: A490 D0F4 D311 A415 3E2B  B7CA DBB8 02B2 58AC D84F
            Subkey fingerprint: BA2C 222F 44AC 00ED 9899  3893 98FE C6BC 752A 3DB6

   Verify date.

If you don't have an OpenPGP key
================================

1. Move to temporary GnuPG directory.

       export GNUPGHOME=$(mktemp -d)

1. Import Tails signing key

       wget https://tails.boum.org/tails-signing.key

       gpg --import < tails-signing.key

1. Install Debian keyring

       sudo apt-get install debian-keyring/jessie

1. Import OpenPGP key of Zack:

       gpg --keyring=/usr/share/keyrings/debian-keyring.gpg --export zack@debian.org | gpg --import

1. Verify that Tails signing key is certified by Zack:

       gpg --check-sigs A490D0F4D311A4153E2BB7CADBB802B258ACD84F

1. Verify ISO image:

       gpg --verify tails-i386-1.6.1.iso.sig tails-i386-1.6.1.iso

   Expected output:

       gpg: Signature made Fri 28 Aug 2015 02:16:10 AM UTC using RSA key ID 752A3DB6
       gpg: Good signature from "Tails developers (offline long-term identity key) <tails@boum.org>"
       gpg: WARNING: This key is not certified with a trusted signature!
       gpg:          There is no indication that the signature belongs to the owner.
       Primary key fingerprint: A490 D0F4 D311 A415 3E2B  B7CA DBB8 02B2 58AC D84F
            Subkey fingerprint: BA2C 222F 44AC 00ED 9899  3893 98FE C6BC 752A 3DB6

   Verify date.

1. Reset GnuPG directory:

       unset GNUPGHOME
